00:03:39.110 --> 00:03:42.040
[Episode 8]

00:03:44.030 --> 00:03:45.750
If you have any questions at school,

00:03:45.750 --> 00:03:46.960
just ask the teachers.

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:48.280
