00:04:21.360 --> 00:04:21.950
Honey.

00:04:22.130 --> 00:04:23.530
Come to the hospital now.

00:04:24.070 --> 00:04:25.530
Mom's in grave condition.

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:37.190
Doctor,

00:04:37.190 --> 00:04:39.000
how did it get so serious all of a sudden?

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:41.400
Wasn't her condition quite stable before?

00:04:41.800 --> 00:04:43.190
The patient needs to rest.

00:04:43.190 --> 00:04:43.870
Officer Wang,

00:04:43.870 --> 00:04:44.730
a word outside.

00:04:56.230 --> 00:04:57.080
Officer Wang,

00:04:57.500 --> 00:04:59.850
your mother is now in serious condition.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:02.050
If we can't find
a suitable kidney donor soon,

00:05:02.050 --> 00:05:02.160
[Quiet]

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:04.220
you'll have to prepare for the worst.

00:05:12.190 --> 00:05:13.250
How is your mother?

00:05:13.950 --> 00:05:15.800
[Quiet]

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:16.860
What are you doing?

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:18.420
I'm trying to help you.

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:19.870
No need.

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:21.680
Why...

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:22.510
are you still mad at me

00:05:22.510 --> 00:05:23.570
at a time like this?

00:05:26.870 --> 00:05:27.930
I've asked around.

00:05:28.360 --> 00:05:29.560
This is a very urgent issue.

00:05:29.560 --> 00:05:32.560
It's extremely hard to find
a proper kidney donor now.

00:05:34.190 --> 00:05:35.430
Why not let me help?

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:37.360
In Hanzhou,

00:05:37.430 --> 00:05:39.360
a three-legged frog might be rare,

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:41.010
but a functional kidney

00:05:41.480 --> 00:05:42.940
shouldn't be hard to find.

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:44.530
What do you want?

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:46.950
Nothing.

00:05:47.510 --> 00:05:49.240
I just like making friends.

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:50.860
I'm helping you

00:05:50.909 --> 00:05:52.240
only because of who you are.

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:53.640
I want nothing in return.

00:05:55.840 --> 00:05:56.560
Luo Bo,

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:58.860
I know you feel guilty.

00:05:59.230 --> 00:06:00.870
But you've chosen the wrong person.

00:06:00.870 --> 00:06:03.200
It's God that has chosen the wrong person.

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:06.240
Your mother raised you all by herself

00:06:06.310 --> 00:06:07.440
with much hardship.

00:06:08.040 --> 00:06:10.130
Of all people, she's the one to get sick.

00:06:10.130 --> 00:06:11.930
Even I feel that's unfair to you.

00:06:12.510 --> 00:06:14.170
Worry about yourself, not me.

00:06:33.040 --> 00:06:33.640
It's okay.

00:06:34.380 --> 00:06:36.290
Just think about whether to make friends

00:06:36.290 --> 00:06:37.490
with me or not.

00:06:38.270 --> 00:06:39.270
But make it quick.

00:06:40.360 --> 00:06:42.430
I heard the hospital nearly issued...

00:06:42.430 --> 00:06:44.260
a critical condition notice.

00:06:50.830 --> 00:06:52.290
When you think it through,

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:53.950
contact me.

00:07:10.690 --> 00:07:14.770
[Hanzhou Central Hospital]

00:07:19.190 --> 00:07:19.720
Tao.

00:07:19.870 --> 00:07:20.730
There you are.

00:07:20.830 --> 00:07:21.800
What are you doing here?

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:23.190
I just spoke with the doctor.

00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:25.040
He asked to wait here
for more information.

00:07:25.040 --> 00:07:26.100
How's your mother?

00:07:27.800 --> 00:07:28.880
Don't worry.

00:07:29.070 --> 00:07:30.750
With nowadays advanced medical care,

00:07:30.750 --> 00:07:31.830
I'm sure your mother will be fine.

00:07:31.830 --> 00:07:33.000
Yes, I know.

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:35.680
My wife made some food for your mother.

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:36.610
It's salt-free.

00:07:37.070 --> 00:07:38.120
This is all we can do

00:07:38.120 --> 00:07:39.320
to help at the moment.

00:07:39.510 --> 00:07:41.400
Thank you. Tell your wife I say thanks.

00:07:41.400 --> 00:07:43.000
Don't even mention it.

00:07:43.240 --> 00:07:45.480
You and your wife
must be swamped these days.

00:07:45.480 --> 00:07:47.380
My wife happened to have time.
She was happy to help.

00:07:47.380 --> 00:07:48.120
Tao,

00:07:49.190 --> 00:07:50.420
take a few days off.

00:07:50.510 --> 00:07:51.600
I've submitted a leave request for you.

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:51.950
No need.

00:07:51.950 --> 00:07:53.430
I've got all my issues in the hospital
sorted out.

00:07:53.430 --> 00:07:55.270
My mom's just waiting for a kidney donor.

00:07:55.270 --> 00:07:56.920
You should keep her company
in the hospital.

00:07:56.920 --> 00:07:59.450
There's adequate manpower
in the office now.

00:08:00.390 --> 00:08:01.310
Any news about

00:08:01.310 --> 00:08:02.310
the kidney donor?

00:08:02.870 --> 00:08:04.390
There's nothing I can do about it.

00:08:04.390 --> 00:08:06.270
All recipients have to wait in line.

00:08:06.270 --> 00:08:06.930
Indeed.

00:08:07.870 --> 00:08:08.850
Don't worry.

00:08:08.950 --> 00:08:10.560
I've prepared money for the surgery.

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:11.240
Wait.

00:08:11.600 --> 00:08:12.860
Let me contribute too.

00:08:12.920 --> 00:08:13.430
No, no.

00:08:13.430 --> 00:08:14.360
I can't borrow money from you,

00:08:14.360 --> 00:08:15.240
because I'm not sure

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:16.260
if I can pay it off.

00:08:16.310 --> 00:08:18.110
Come on, aren't we good friends?

00:08:18.120 --> 00:08:18.800
We are,

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:20.390
but money is not the problem here.

00:08:20.390 --> 00:08:22.310
I don't even mind selling my house,

00:08:22.310 --> 00:08:23.510
as long as my mom can be cured.

00:08:23.510 --> 00:08:25.270
Don't sell your house. Just let us help.

00:08:25.270 --> 00:08:26.160
Anything else can wait
until after the surgery.

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:28.430
I have quite a few acquaintances
working in hospitals.

00:08:28.430 --> 00:08:30.560
I was out seeking help the entire time
when my father was ill,

00:08:30.560 --> 00:08:31.800
and thus built many connections.

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:32.240
How about

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:34.760
we consult another specialist?

00:08:35.390 --> 00:08:36.429
Sounds good.

00:08:36.450 --> 00:08:38.380
Ji, please inquire about it for me.

00:08:40.590 --> 00:08:41.280
Shall we go?

00:08:41.510 --> 00:08:42.000
Let's visit Tao's mother.

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:42.440
Sure.

00:08:42.440 --> 00:08:42.919
Right.

00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:43.750
We couldn't find her.

00:08:43.750 --> 00:08:44.480
Where is she?

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:45.750
-That way?
-No, this way.

00:08:45.750 --> 00:08:46.390
This way?

00:08:46.390 --> 00:08:46.870
Yes.

00:08:46.870 --> 00:08:48.360
I was just telling Ji we went too far.

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:48.960
Mr. Luo!

00:08:51.630 --> 00:08:52.150
Mr. Ma.

00:08:54.910 --> 00:08:55.570
Have a seat.

00:08:57.390 --> 00:08:59.000
What's with the online gaming company?

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:00.040
What went wrong?

00:09:00.270 --> 00:09:01.300
I'm puzzled too.

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:03.360
Could Scar and his people

00:09:03.360 --> 00:09:04.290
have confessed?

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:05.350
No way.

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:07.440
Scar has worked for me for many years

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:08.700
and been through a lot.

00:09:08.910 --> 00:09:10.840
He's tighter-lipped than anyone.

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:14.250
People are unpredictable.

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:15.970
You can't fully trust them.

00:09:16.630 --> 00:09:17.980
Cut that crap.

00:09:19.390 --> 00:09:20.480
You would've got in trouble already

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:21.880
if I hadn't reminded you.

00:09:22.630 --> 00:09:23.630
It was you who raised the idea

00:09:23.630 --> 00:09:25.150
and engaged Qian Yuhong in this.

00:09:25.150 --> 00:09:27.100
The mistake must be on your side.

00:09:27.270 --> 00:09:28.330
Mr. Luo, calm down.

00:09:29.030 --> 00:09:29.830
The root cause

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:31.030
of this predicament

00:09:31.030 --> 00:09:32.960
is Qin Feng—such a pain in the neck.

00:09:34.870 --> 00:09:36.150
Weren't those establishments

00:09:36.150 --> 00:09:37.150
of yours shut down

00:09:37.450 --> 00:09:39.250
by Qin Feng not long ago, Mr. Luo?

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:40.890
I've cleaned up my own mess,

00:09:41.790 --> 00:09:44.100
while yours is yet to be dealt with.

00:09:44.670 --> 00:09:45.870
Mr. Luo, at this time,

00:09:46.390 --> 00:09:48.550
it's pointless to hurl insults
at each other.

00:09:48.550 --> 00:09:50.550
The priority is to solve the problem.

00:09:50.550 --> 00:09:51.080
We've

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:52.550
suffered financial losses,

00:09:52.550 --> 00:09:54.480
but Qin Feng hasn't found any evidence.

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:55.360
So, I think

00:09:55.670 --> 00:09:56.330
all is fine.

00:09:56.440 --> 00:09:58.120
Tell Qian Yuhong to turn herself in.

00:09:58.120 --> 00:09:59.390
That's not necessary at the moment, is it?

00:09:59.390 --> 00:10:00.960
It takes time to prepare witnesses,

00:10:00.960 --> 00:10:03.820
evidence and testimonies in advance.
Understood?

00:10:03.910 --> 00:10:04.600
Or how do you say

00:10:04.600 --> 00:10:06.510
we should put an end to this whole thing?

00:10:06.510 --> 00:10:07.080
Enough.

00:10:09.150 --> 00:10:10.810
They haven't traced to us now,

00:10:10.870 --> 00:10:13.070
but it doesn't mean they won't forever.

00:10:13.870 --> 00:10:14.440
We must

00:10:14.600 --> 00:10:16.170
extricate ourselves soon.

00:10:16.870 --> 00:10:17.600
We can't

00:10:18.510 --> 00:10:21.110
let the police find anyone
beyond Qian Yuhong.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.150
Rest assured, Mr. Ma.

00:10:24.150 --> 00:10:26.550
I've done proper preparation beforehand.

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:27.520
Bole Finance

00:10:27.630 --> 00:10:28.720
is by no means legally

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:31.180
associated with the online gaming company.

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:32.700
Hao,

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:34.720
I know you are

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:36.790
somewhat into Qian Yuhong.

00:10:37.030 --> 00:10:38.250
But I'm warning you,

00:10:39.390 --> 00:10:41.390
don't let your affection for a woman

00:10:41.790 --> 00:10:43.250
obstruct our great cause.

00:10:43.360 --> 00:10:45.760
In this regard, Luo truly outperforms you.

00:10:45.790 --> 00:10:46.240
Yes.

00:10:46.550 --> 00:10:47.750
You're right, Mr. Ma.

00:10:48.270 --> 00:10:48.960
It was I who founded

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:51.080
the online gaming company for the group.

00:10:51.080 --> 00:10:52.080
It's very secure.

00:10:52.200 --> 00:10:53.240
Once things quiet down,

00:10:53.240 --> 00:10:54.740
I can start over anytime.

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:59.400
I do appreciate that perspective of yours.

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:00.970
Luo Bo,

00:11:01.080 --> 00:11:02.080
you should really

00:11:02.080 --> 00:11:03.870
learn from Hao about certain things.

00:11:03.870 --> 00:11:04.510
Got it?

00:11:04.630 --> 00:11:05.000
Mr. Ma,

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.270
I'm very much flattered.

00:11:06.270 --> 00:11:08.360
I've just read a few more books
than others.

00:11:08.360 --> 00:11:09.230
Mr. Luo has more

00:11:09.550 --> 00:11:11.560
practical experience than I do.

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:13.200
I should learn from him in this respect.

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:14.200
No, no, no.

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:16.350
Mr. Song is tremendously...

00:11:16.550 --> 00:11:17.480
knowledgeable.

00:11:17.910 --> 00:11:19.840
You're just being modest, Mr. Luo.

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:20.750
Take

00:11:21.510 --> 00:11:22.120
Larry Page

00:11:22.960 --> 00:11:24.490
and Steve Jobs as examples.

00:11:24.510 --> 00:11:26.480
They both dropped out
to start their businesses

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:29.390
and became outstanding entrepreneurs
in the end, right?

00:11:29.390 --> 00:11:30.870
You're just like them, Mr. Ma.

00:11:30.870 --> 00:11:32.870
Heroes could come from all origins.

00:11:34.270 --> 00:11:35.100
Well said.

00:11:35.440 --> 00:11:36.300
Very well said.

00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:39.400
Keep up the good work.

00:11:39.550 --> 00:11:41.760
The future depends on you young people.

00:11:42.910 --> 00:11:43.320
Mr. Ma,

00:11:43.710 --> 00:11:45.040
I'll take my leave then.

00:11:45.240 --> 00:11:46.860
I will meet with Yuhong

00:11:46.960 --> 00:11:47.620
and give her

00:11:47.790 --> 00:11:49.050
proper instructions.

00:11:50.200 --> 00:11:50.630
Okay.

00:12:00.550 --> 00:12:01.390
Later on,

00:12:02.240 --> 00:12:03.260
have your people

00:12:03.440 --> 00:12:05.100
keep an eye on Qian Yuhong.

00:12:06.080 --> 00:12:07.600
You need to protect yourself from danger.

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:08.310
Got it?

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:09.200
Got it.

00:12:11.210 --> 00:12:13.020
What about Ye Tianyou's nephew?

00:12:13.150 --> 00:12:14.390
Rest assured. He's been on the hook.

00:12:14.390 --> 00:12:16.720
We just need to pull the fishing rod
at the right time.

00:12:16.720 --> 00:12:17.840
I'm also sourcing a kidney

00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:19.100
for Wang Tao's mother.

00:12:19.360 --> 00:12:20.840
When one is found,

00:12:21.270 --> 00:12:24.400
I don't believe he'll reject it
and watch his mother die.

00:12:25.200 --> 00:12:26.240
Remember,

00:12:27.120 --> 00:12:29.050
the more you know about your rival,

00:12:29.440 --> 00:12:31.700
the higher your chances of winning.

00:12:32.600 --> 00:12:33.000
Got it.

00:12:57.320 --> 00:12:57.840
Tianye,

00:12:58.840 --> 00:12:59.550
I heard

00:12:59.670 --> 00:13:02.330
the police raided
the Rainbow Network Company.

00:13:02.910 --> 00:13:03.480
But Yuhong

00:13:03.480 --> 00:13:05.210
and Song Hao weren't affected.

00:13:05.550 --> 00:13:07.550
I believe
Qin Feng will bring them to justice.

00:13:07.550 --> 00:13:09.200
But we can't sit back and do nothing.

00:13:09.200 --> 00:13:10.130
We must help him.

00:13:10.320 --> 00:13:10.840
But Feng said...

00:13:10.840 --> 00:13:11.600
Listen to me.

00:13:12.270 --> 00:13:13.600
You just stay with Luo Bo

00:13:13.670 --> 00:13:16.070
and keep close watch
on Song Hao and Yuhong.

00:13:17.630 --> 00:13:18.080
Yes.

00:13:26.240 --> 00:13:27.240
What do you think?

00:13:27.550 --> 00:13:28.510
I think it's nice.

00:13:28.510 --> 00:13:29.910
The ventilation's good.

00:13:30.120 --> 00:13:31.670
More importantly,
sunlight can get through,

00:13:31.670 --> 00:13:32.000
right?

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:33.730
Uncle and you can bask in the sun

00:13:33.790 --> 00:13:34.840
in the living room or the balcony.

00:13:34.840 --> 00:13:35.440
That's cozy,

00:13:35.440 --> 00:13:35.970
isn't it?

00:13:36.630 --> 00:13:38.960
Siyuan, this will be your room.

00:13:38.960 --> 00:13:40.000
There's even a place for me?

00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:41.390
The apartment also comes with a study.

00:13:41.390 --> 00:13:42.990
-Auntie, then I...
-Siyuan!

00:13:46.360 --> 00:13:47.960
Mr. Song.

00:13:47.960 --> 00:13:49.600
Why are you still calling me Mr. Song?

00:13:49.600 --> 00:13:50.240
Didn't I tell you

00:13:50.240 --> 00:13:51.040
to call me Hao?

00:13:51.630 --> 00:13:52.760
Sure. Hao.

00:13:52.960 --> 00:13:53.790
What are you doing here?

00:13:53.790 --> 00:13:54.990
Addressing an issue.

00:13:55.320 --> 00:13:56.250
Who's this lady?

00:13:57.000 --> 00:13:57.870
Allow me to introduce

00:13:57.870 --> 00:13:58.670
my aunt to you.

00:13:59.080 --> 00:14:00.150
This is Song Hao,

00:14:00.360 --> 00:14:01.360
an enterpreneur.

00:14:01.390 --> 00:14:02.450
Let's sit and talk.

00:14:02.550 --> 00:14:02.840
Well,

00:14:02.840 --> 00:14:04.120
do you...

00:14:04.720 --> 00:14:05.550
also own

00:14:06.150 --> 00:14:07.200
this development?

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:07.790
No.

00:14:07.790 --> 00:14:09.030
This project belongs to Jinding.

00:14:09.030 --> 00:14:10.690
My company has invested in it.

00:14:12.150 --> 00:14:12.790
I have to say

00:14:12.790 --> 00:14:14.200
these apartments are really nice.

00:14:14.200 --> 00:14:14.510
I agree.

00:14:14.510 --> 00:14:15.370
Right, Auntie?

00:14:16.150 --> 00:14:16.720
Look,

00:14:17.240 --> 00:14:18.640
my aunt is thinking about

00:14:18.670 --> 00:14:19.670
buying an apartment

00:14:19.670 --> 00:14:21.510
for better living conditions.

00:14:21.870 --> 00:14:22.510
You see,

00:14:22.510 --> 00:14:23.570
my uncle is about to

00:14:23.790 --> 00:14:24.480
retire.

00:14:25.030 --> 00:14:26.430
The two of them would like

00:14:26.550 --> 00:14:28.680
a comfortable abode for their old age.

00:14:29.480 --> 00:14:30.730
But the problem is...

00:14:32.670 --> 00:14:34.390
The price is a bit too high.

00:14:35.960 --> 00:14:37.250
That's easy to fix.

00:14:37.600 --> 00:14:39.600
I'm friends with the sales manager.

00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:40.480
Ma'am,

00:14:40.790 --> 00:14:41.720
with my help,

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:44.400
you'll get a 30% discount if you put down

00:14:44.960 --> 00:14:45.890
a deposit today.

00:14:45.960 --> 00:14:47.420
Auntie, what do you think?

00:14:47.870 --> 00:14:48.510
Siyuan,

00:14:49.390 --> 00:14:50.870
that 30% discount

00:14:50.870 --> 00:14:52.080
will save me much money.

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:52.550
Indeed.

00:14:53.630 --> 00:14:54.360
How about...

00:14:55.080 --> 00:14:56.750
you pay a deposit now?

00:14:59.720 --> 00:15:00.370
Maybe

00:15:00.440 --> 00:15:02.770
I should discuss it with your uncle first.

00:15:03.000 --> 00:15:04.260
Laugh at me if you want.

00:15:04.720 --> 00:15:05.870
To be frank, your uncle

00:15:05.870 --> 00:15:07.530
manages all family finances.

00:15:08.390 --> 00:15:09.440
I understand.

00:15:09.550 --> 00:15:10.440
Uncle lives

00:15:10.440 --> 00:15:11.630
a frugal life.

00:15:12.550 --> 00:15:14.810
He disdains the idea of squandering money.

00:15:14.810 --> 00:15:15.440
I get it.

00:15:16.670 --> 00:15:17.730
As for the deposit,

00:15:17.960 --> 00:15:18.820
I'll handle it.

00:15:20.790 --> 00:15:22.440
How can I trouble you with that?

00:15:22.440 --> 00:15:24.040
I'm just doing what I should.

00:15:24.200 --> 00:15:25.860
I see it as my responsibility.

00:15:27.870 --> 00:15:28.480
Hao!

00:15:29.030 --> 00:15:29.630
Thank you.

00:15:30.080 --> 00:15:30.750
We're like family.

00:15:30.750 --> 00:15:31.320
No need for formalities.

00:15:31.320 --> 00:15:31.910
Okay.

00:15:59.550 --> 00:16:00.130
Sir,

00:16:00.390 --> 00:16:01.940
many thanks for your tips

00:16:02.030 --> 00:16:03.890
about the online gaming company.

00:16:06.440 --> 00:16:07.300
I'm sorry, sir.

00:16:08.360 --> 00:16:09.360
But rest assured,

00:16:09.630 --> 00:16:10.630
all upcoming problems

00:16:10.630 --> 00:16:12.390
will be solved as soon as possible.

00:16:12.390 --> 00:16:13.240
I'll also quicken my pace

00:16:13.240 --> 00:16:14.840
with the plans for Ye Siyuan.

00:16:15.480 --> 00:16:17.810
Here is a little present prepared for you.

00:16:18.270 --> 00:16:19.530
It's made of pure gold.

00:16:19.720 --> 00:16:20.850
Hope you'll like it.

00:16:22.010 --> 00:16:23.340
I'll leave it here then.

00:16:26.030 --> 00:16:26.870
I'm supposed to

00:16:26.870 --> 00:16:28.390
collect a surveillance device from you,

00:16:28.390 --> 00:16:29.000
right?

00:16:33.510 --> 00:16:34.200
Orchids.

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:37.050
Director Ye will surely like them.

00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:52.550
Make the final payment on the apartment
within the next few days.

00:16:52.550 --> 00:16:54.880
Transfer the ownership to your aunt soon.

00:16:55.960 --> 00:16:56.550
Thanks.

00:16:59.870 --> 00:17:01.730
My uncle wants to see me tomorrow.

00:17:02.600 --> 00:17:03.790
Has he figured out...

00:17:03.790 --> 00:17:04.880
this purchase?

00:17:04.880 --> 00:17:06.190
Don't worry.

00:17:06.480 --> 00:17:08.140
I'll tell you what to do later.

00:17:08.960 --> 00:17:11.619
Take this pot of flowers with you
when you leave.

00:17:13.790 --> 00:17:14.920
Why?

00:17:17.849 --> 00:17:19.450
It's your uncle's favorite,

00:17:20.310 --> 00:17:21.770
and your initiation task.

00:17:30.960 --> 00:17:31.480
Uncle,

00:17:31.720 --> 00:17:33.050
I know you like orchids,

00:17:33.160 --> 00:17:34.240
so I specially brought you some.

00:17:34.240 --> 00:17:35.170
I'll put it here.

00:17:40.310 --> 00:17:41.170
Close the door.

00:17:45.830 --> 00:17:46.350
Uncle,

00:17:48.440 --> 00:17:49.070
what's up?

00:17:51.400 --> 00:17:52.200
Let me ask you.

00:17:52.920 --> 00:17:53.750
Have you been

00:17:53.750 --> 00:17:55.790
hanging out with Luo Bo and Song Hao a lot

00:17:55.790 --> 00:17:56.640
recently?

00:17:59.510 --> 00:18:00.170
Those guys?

00:18:01.070 --> 00:18:02.000
Anything wrong?

00:18:03.550 --> 00:18:06.210
I'm asking
if you've been hanging out with them.

00:18:09.400 --> 00:18:11.030
When I studied abroad,
a schoolmate of mine

00:18:11.030 --> 00:18:12.310
happened to know Song Hao.

00:18:12.310 --> 00:18:14.510
He was then introduced to me over a meal.

00:18:14.680 --> 00:18:15.940
I'm not close with him.

00:18:17.750 --> 00:18:19.370
Did they ask you anything?

00:18:20.030 --> 00:18:20.730
No.

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:22.530
We just had a meal together.

00:18:22.690 --> 00:18:23.880
There were many other guests.

00:18:23.880 --> 00:18:25.210
I barely got to know him.

00:18:25.590 --> 00:18:27.110
Have you forgotten what I told you

00:18:27.110 --> 00:18:27.680
before?

00:18:30.440 --> 00:18:31.240
No, I haven't.

00:18:32.470 --> 00:18:33.830
You told me to choose my friends wisely,

00:18:33.830 --> 00:18:35.050
especially

00:18:35.510 --> 00:18:36.880
in a Hanzhou.

00:18:39.350 --> 00:18:40.350
Keep this in mind:

00:18:40.400 --> 00:18:41.060
from now on,

00:18:41.310 --> 00:18:43.240
do not interact with them anymore.

00:18:44.030 --> 00:18:46.430
Hanging with them
won't bring you any good.

00:18:48.270 --> 00:18:49.800
I have a lot going on lately.

00:18:52.000 --> 00:18:52.800
I'm very busy.

00:18:54.400 --> 00:18:55.750
Stay in your hometown for now.

00:18:55.750 --> 00:18:57.880
Don't come back until some time later.

00:18:58.640 --> 00:19:00.480
Uncle, I've only been here for a few days.

00:19:00.480 --> 00:19:01.680
Let me play in Hanzhou for...

00:19:01.680 --> 00:19:02.280
No, I mean,

00:19:02.830 --> 00:19:04.750
I'd like to keep Auntie company.

00:19:05.750 --> 00:19:06.350
Enough.

00:19:06.440 --> 00:19:07.040
Off you go.

00:19:08.310 --> 00:19:10.040
Fine. I'm leaving then, Uncle.

00:19:13.000 --> 00:19:14.730
I've placed the orchids there!

00:19:29.350 --> 00:19:32.790
[Hanzhou Rural Commercial Bank]

00:19:41.860 --> 00:19:42.680
Mr. Luo,

00:19:43.770 --> 00:19:45.030
Yuhong entered a bank.

00:19:45.250 --> 00:19:47.310
It seems she's carrying a bag of cash.

00:19:47.640 --> 00:19:48.350
Rest assured.

00:19:48.350 --> 00:19:49.480
We're watching her.

00:20:01.680 --> 00:20:02.430
Who are you?

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:03.750
Let go of me!

00:20:03.920 --> 00:20:04.550
Let go!

00:20:04.830 --> 00:20:05.490
Let go of me!

00:20:05.550 --> 00:20:06.550
Help!

00:20:06.920 --> 00:20:07.720
Help!

00:20:24.880 --> 00:20:26.610
Come with me if you want to live.

00:20:31.350 --> 00:20:33.410
[Hanzhou Taxi]

00:20:33.410 --> 00:20:35.470
Don't you know someone plans to kill you?

00:20:35.470 --> 00:20:36.430
Who are you?

00:20:36.960 --> 00:20:38.290
Where are you taking me?

00:20:39.200 --> 00:20:39.970
Don't worry.

00:20:40.720 --> 00:20:42.030
I mean no harm to you.

00:20:43.240 --> 00:20:44.160
In fact,

00:20:44.880 --> 00:20:46.640
I hope we can help each other.

00:20:47.440 --> 00:20:49.840
You're eager
to get out of Luo Bo's control,

00:20:50.110 --> 00:20:50.770
aren't you?

00:20:53.070 --> 00:20:54.130
"Help each other"?

00:20:55.250 --> 00:20:56.850
Why are you saying this to me?

00:20:56.960 --> 00:20:57.890
What do you want?

00:20:59.680 --> 00:21:00.510
We're both smart.

00:21:00.510 --> 00:21:02.110
Let's level with each other.

00:21:03.270 --> 00:21:05.200
You've done many things for Luo Bo.

00:21:05.480 --> 00:21:08.010
Do you think
he'll easily let you off the hook?

00:21:09.510 --> 00:21:10.240
To be honest,

00:21:11.110 --> 00:21:11.970
I had a brother,

00:21:12.680 --> 00:21:14.080
who was a police officer.

00:21:14.400 --> 00:21:16.350
He died just for the reason

00:21:17.070 --> 00:21:18.670
that he stood in Luo Bo's way.

00:21:19.070 --> 00:21:19.930
Do you think...

00:21:20.270 --> 00:21:21.470
Luo Bo will spare you?

00:21:22.880 --> 00:21:23.960
You actually

00:21:24.880 --> 00:21:26.390
remind me of a girl I knew.

00:21:26.960 --> 00:21:27.620
She danced,

00:21:29.000 --> 00:21:30.000
marvelously.

00:21:31.250 --> 00:21:32.790
If she hadn't died,

00:21:33.640 --> 00:21:35.840
she would be a professional dancer now.

00:21:36.350 --> 00:21:37.560
You're about her age.

00:21:39.410 --> 00:21:41.470
She was left with no choice but to die.

00:21:43.000 --> 00:21:44.400
Not being able to help her

00:21:44.960 --> 00:21:46.760
is the biggest regret in my life.

00:21:49.520 --> 00:21:50.920
Only by taking down Luo Bo

00:21:51.680 --> 00:21:53.610
will you stand a chance to survive.

00:21:56.420 --> 00:21:58.020
You don't have to believe me.

00:21:59.240 --> 00:22:02.100
But you should at least believe
justice does exist,

00:22:02.310 --> 00:22:02.790
right?

00:22:05.270 --> 00:22:06.070
Think it over.

00:22:11.200 --> 00:22:12.040
Qian Yuhong,

00:22:12.110 --> 00:22:14.040
everyone calls you Yuhong, right?

00:22:14.880 --> 00:22:15.350
Yes.

00:22:15.830 --> 00:22:17.350
You work

00:22:17.750 --> 00:22:19.510
in the Rainbow Network Company.

00:22:19.510 --> 00:22:21.110
What position do you hold?

00:22:21.790 --> 00:22:22.870
What company?

00:22:24.310 --> 00:22:25.310
Never heard of it.

00:22:25.590 --> 00:22:27.050
Rainbow Network Company.

00:22:27.640 --> 00:22:28.370
I don't know.

00:22:28.510 --> 00:22:29.960
I have nothing to do with it.

00:22:29.960 --> 00:22:32.690
Today, at the bank entrance,
there were 3 people.

00:22:32.750 --> 00:22:33.680
Do you know them?

00:22:35.590 --> 00:22:36.790
I had never seen them before today.

00:22:36.790 --> 00:22:38.200
But you do realize
what they were trying to do

00:22:38.200 --> 00:22:39.330
to you today, right?

00:22:39.350 --> 00:22:41.550
You know what they were up to, don't you?

00:22:43.510 --> 00:22:44.710
Let me put it this way.

00:22:45.590 --> 00:22:46.550
Today,

00:22:47.160 --> 00:22:49.460
you were lucky that my colleague was there

00:22:49.460 --> 00:22:50.810
to save you.

00:22:52.030 --> 00:22:54.090
Otherwise, nobody could say for sure

00:22:54.270 --> 00:22:55.310
where you would be

00:22:55.880 --> 00:22:57.590
and what you would go through now.

00:22:57.590 --> 00:22:59.520
You probably know better than I do.

00:23:00.240 --> 00:23:02.170
We brought you here because we hope

00:23:02.590 --> 00:23:04.790
you can cooperate with our investigation,

00:23:04.790 --> 00:23:05.920
and also because...

00:23:07.190 --> 00:23:08.750
this is a way to protect you.

00:23:09.440 --> 00:23:12.240
It's not easy for a young woman
to make a living in this vast world.

00:23:12.240 --> 00:23:13.170
You have a father

00:23:13.590 --> 00:23:14.750
and a younger brother

00:23:14.750 --> 00:23:15.480
at home.

00:23:16.160 --> 00:23:17.560
I don't know if incidents

00:23:18.060 --> 00:23:19.220
like the one today

00:23:19.510 --> 00:23:20.940
often take place.

00:23:21.180 --> 00:23:21.790
But judging from

00:23:21.790 --> 00:23:23.790
how brazen and bold they've become,

00:23:26.240 --> 00:23:28.640
when you leave the Public Security Bureau,

00:23:29.790 --> 00:23:31.790
I'm not sure what will happen to you.

00:23:33.510 --> 00:23:35.320
Now, I'll ask you again.

00:23:35.350 --> 00:23:38.720
In the Rainbow Network Co., Ltd.,

00:23:38.920 --> 00:23:40.830
exactly what position do you hold,

00:23:40.830 --> 00:23:41.830
and what do you do?

00:23:54.880 --> 00:23:55.920
Actually, I...

00:23:57.090 --> 00:23:57.790
don't know how...

00:23:57.790 --> 00:23:58.350
Zhong.

00:23:59.070 --> 00:24:00.590
Here are the files
on that online gaming company.

00:24:00.590 --> 00:24:01.960
See if they're useful to you.

00:24:01.960 --> 00:24:02.730
Director Peng.

00:24:02.730 --> 00:24:03.590
Director Peng.

00:24:03.890 --> 00:24:04.520
Let me take them.

00:24:04.520 --> 00:24:07.120
[Archives]

00:24:12.200 --> 00:24:12.930
Here you are.

00:24:13.800 --> 00:24:16.230
I spent much effort
attaining this bracelet

00:24:16.230 --> 00:24:17.430
from Master Jingxin.

00:24:18.110 --> 00:24:19.910
Who on earth are you giving it to?

00:24:23.960 --> 00:24:25.560
A friend in the police force.

00:24:25.920 --> 00:24:27.320
He loves trinkets alike.

00:24:58.110 --> 00:24:58.840
Qian Yuhong,

00:25:00.550 --> 00:25:02.810
Remaining silent won't make the problem

00:25:04.310 --> 00:25:04.920
go away.

00:25:06.160 --> 00:25:07.650
We will eventually figure out

00:25:07.650 --> 00:25:08.640
all financial transactions

00:25:08.640 --> 00:25:10.000
and track down the funds

00:25:10.750 --> 00:25:13.010
wired from the Rainbow Network Company.

00:25:13.830 --> 00:25:16.360
No matter
how tight your criminal network is,

00:25:17.070 --> 00:25:18.470
there must be weak spots.

00:25:22.590 --> 00:25:23.470
Officer,

00:25:23.750 --> 00:25:25.030
I'd like to reiterate

00:25:25.140 --> 00:25:27.080
that I've never heard about
this network company

00:25:27.080 --> 00:25:28.410
you just mentioned.

00:25:28.430 --> 00:25:29.020
Also,

00:25:29.790 --> 00:25:30.790
I don't know any of the people

00:25:30.790 --> 00:25:31.960
you asked me about.

00:25:32.470 --> 00:25:33.790
If you have any evidence,

00:25:33.790 --> 00:25:34.680
arrest me right now.

00:25:34.680 --> 00:25:35.480
If not...

00:25:36.400 --> 00:25:38.460
let me go, as I'm very busy these days.

00:25:41.560 --> 00:25:43.290
Do you have any other question?

00:26:02.000 --> 00:26:02.720
This is odd.

00:26:02.720 --> 00:26:04.480
I could tell
she was about to confess just now.

00:26:04.480 --> 00:26:05.410
Why suddenly...

00:26:09.680 --> 00:26:11.620
Find out her parents' address.

00:26:19.500 --> 00:26:20.160
Qian Yuhong

00:26:20.160 --> 00:26:21.750
was just brought
to the Public Security Bureau.

00:26:21.750 --> 00:26:22.590
Qin Feng

00:26:22.590 --> 00:26:23.850
nearly broke her down.

00:26:24.440 --> 00:26:25.200
This woman

00:26:25.830 --> 00:26:27.230
must be eliminated soon.

00:26:28.270 --> 00:26:28.880
Got it.

00:26:29.270 --> 00:26:30.200
I'm sorry, sir,

00:26:30.440 --> 00:26:31.840
for causing you trouble.

00:26:37.440 --> 00:26:38.920
The two of you, go catch

00:26:38.920 --> 00:26:40.440
Qian Yuhong's father and brother.

00:26:40.440 --> 00:26:41.240
What's wrong, Bo?

00:26:41.240 --> 00:26:42.070
Do as I say!

00:26:42.720 --> 00:26:43.270
Yes!

00:26:47.350 --> 00:26:48.590
Call Song Hao.

00:26:49.200 --> 00:26:50.260
Have him come over.

00:26:50.480 --> 00:26:51.210
Yes, Mr. Luo.

00:27:01.400 --> 00:27:02.160
Let go of me!

00:27:05.510 --> 00:27:06.470
What is this for?

00:27:06.680 --> 00:27:07.480
Hands off!

00:27:07.920 --> 00:27:08.350
Move it!

00:27:08.350 --> 00:27:08.960
Let me go!

00:27:08.960 --> 00:27:10.000
Let go of my son!

00:27:10.480 --> 00:27:11.340
Let go of my son!

00:27:11.510 --> 00:27:12.400
Let go of my son!

00:27:13.790 --> 00:27:14.480
Let go of me!

00:27:14.550 --> 00:27:15.110
Hands off my son!

00:27:15.110 --> 00:27:15.720
Freeze!

00:27:15.880 --> 00:27:16.940
Leave my son alone!

00:27:17.000 --> 00:27:17.550
Let me go!

00:27:17.550 --> 00:27:18.410
Let go of my son!

00:27:22.070 --> 00:27:22.670
Stay down!

00:27:26.440 --> 00:27:27.070
Don't move!

00:27:27.070 --> 00:27:27.730
Let go of me!

00:27:29.030 --> 00:27:30.750
We're police. Don't be afraid.

00:27:30.750 --> 00:27:32.810
You're Qian Yuhong's family, right?

00:27:55.160 --> 00:27:55.790
Mr. Ma,

00:27:56.200 --> 00:27:56.960
what happened?

00:27:56.960 --> 00:27:58.020
What did Yuhong do?

00:27:58.750 --> 00:27:59.810
She planned to flee

00:28:01.070 --> 00:28:02.790
After she made a deposit with a bank,

00:28:02.790 --> 00:28:05.070
Qin Feng took her
to the Public Security Bureau.

00:28:05.070 --> 00:28:06.200
She nearly confessed.

00:28:06.200 --> 00:28:08.350
That's impossible.
Why would she try to flee?

00:28:08.350 --> 00:28:09.150
I'll call her.

00:28:24.590 --> 00:28:25.990
I took every precaution,

00:28:26.480 --> 00:28:28.350
including sending people to her home.

00:28:28.350 --> 00:28:31.200
But her family were taken away
by Qin Feng in the end.

00:28:31.200 --> 00:28:32.150
Now, her entire family

00:28:32.150 --> 00:28:33.810
has completely disappeared.

00:28:34.830 --> 00:28:37.690
If Qian Yuhong
wasn't cooperating with the police,

00:28:37.920 --> 00:28:40.180
why would the police protect her family?

00:28:43.790 --> 00:28:44.310
Mr. Ma,

00:28:45.110 --> 00:28:46.790
could it be a misunderstanding?

00:28:46.790 --> 00:28:48.920
Everyone should clean up his own mess.

00:28:49.160 --> 00:28:50.560
Qian Yuhong is your aide.

00:28:51.200 --> 00:28:51.750
Mr. Ma,

00:28:52.450 --> 00:28:54.350
things haven't gotten this serious, right?

00:28:54.350 --> 00:28:56.590
Besides, the police
are keeping close watch on us.

00:28:56.590 --> 00:28:57.920
If anything goes wrong,

00:28:58.110 --> 00:28:59.970
you'll be implicated, won't you?

00:29:00.030 --> 00:29:00.630
Is that so?

00:29:10.550 --> 00:29:13.080
You're still reluctant
to make a real effort.

00:29:13.610 --> 00:29:14.110
Mr. Ma.

00:29:14.960 --> 00:29:15.510
Mr. Ma.

00:29:16.310 --> 00:29:17.400
You take care of this matter

00:29:17.400 --> 00:29:18.730
regarding Qian Yuhong.

00:29:21.700 --> 00:29:22.750
Where is Qian Yuhong?

00:29:22.750 --> 00:29:23.480
I don't know.

00:29:24.960 --> 00:29:25.670
Lin,

00:29:25.690 --> 00:29:27.020
He says he doesn't know.

00:29:28.270 --> 00:29:29.200
What do you mean?

00:29:49.270 --> 00:29:50.730
I'll ask you one more time.

00:29:51.160 --> 00:29:52.360
Where is Qian Yuhong?

00:29:52.890 --> 00:29:54.020
Guanlan Residence.

00:29:54.510 --> 00:29:55.150
Mr. Ma,

00:29:55.510 --> 00:29:56.940
I'll talk to her.

00:29:57.000 --> 00:29:59.060
I promise she'll keep her mouth shut!

00:30:00.270 --> 00:30:01.200
Lin, go with him.

00:30:34.550 --> 00:30:35.110
Dad.

00:30:35.750 --> 00:30:36.310
Yuhong,

00:30:36.490 --> 00:30:37.290
where are you?

00:30:38.310 --> 00:30:40.160
I'm home. What's wrong?

00:30:40.240 --> 00:30:40.950
Have you

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:42.660
got in any trouble lately?

00:30:43.050 --> 00:30:43.870
This afternoon,

00:30:43.870 --> 00:30:45.240
some people came to our home

00:30:45.240 --> 00:30:46.040
and nearly

00:30:46.070 --> 00:30:47.610
kidnapped your brother.

00:30:47.630 --> 00:30:48.310
Fortunately,

00:30:48.310 --> 00:30:50.110
two officers came to our rescue.

00:30:52.240 --> 00:30:54.480
You're saying
two police officers came to your rescue?

00:30:54.480 --> 00:30:55.280
That's right.

00:30:55.380 --> 00:30:57.580
They were Officer Qin and Officer Wang.

00:30:58.670 --> 00:30:59.320
We're

00:30:59.350 --> 00:31:01.150
with them right now.

00:31:01.880 --> 00:31:03.400
Oh, right. Yuhong, wait a second.

00:31:03.400 --> 00:31:05.510
Officer Qin wants a word with you.

00:31:06.030 --> 00:31:06.760
Officer Qin.

00:31:10.330 --> 00:31:11.170
Qian Yuhong,

00:31:11.960 --> 00:31:13.090
where are my family?

00:31:13.750 --> 00:31:16.220
They're at the police station now,

00:31:16.400 --> 00:31:17.260
safe and sound.

00:31:17.440 --> 00:31:18.770
Don't worry about them.

00:31:19.560 --> 00:31:20.830
Thank you, Officer Qin.

00:31:20.830 --> 00:31:21.760
You're welcome.

00:31:22.110 --> 00:31:23.710
I'm only fulfilling my duty.

00:31:24.330 --> 00:31:26.330
Please leave me alone, Officer Qin.

00:31:27.070 --> 00:31:29.400
I really can't afford to cross those guys.

00:31:30.770 --> 00:31:31.540
Qian Yuhong,

00:31:32.360 --> 00:31:33.820
I'll say this to you again.

00:31:34.460 --> 00:31:37.000
Even if you take the fall for them,

00:31:37.750 --> 00:31:39.810
they still won't let you off the hook.

00:31:39.950 --> 00:31:40.990
In other words,

00:31:41.550 --> 00:31:43.720
though I've brought your family here
today,

00:31:43.720 --> 00:31:45.160
there's no way they can

00:31:45.160 --> 00:31:47.160
stay in the police station forever.

00:31:47.930 --> 00:31:49.260
You get that, don't you?

00:31:50.110 --> 00:31:51.200
But what if I tell you

00:31:51.200 --> 00:31:53.110
their claws have reached you?

00:31:54.350 --> 00:31:55.280
What do you mean?

00:31:57.510 --> 00:31:59.830
Previously, in the Public Security Bureau,

00:31:59.830 --> 00:32:01.350
the officer seated next to you

00:32:01.350 --> 00:32:02.210
could be a mole.

00:32:02.510 --> 00:32:03.510
He wore a bracelet

00:32:04.000 --> 00:32:05.260
that was a gift from me.

00:32:08.240 --> 00:32:09.100
Who do you mean?

00:32:10.080 --> 00:32:11.410
I'm sorry, Officer Qin.

00:32:11.430 --> 00:32:12.960
I don't want to go to prison.

00:32:18.070 --> 00:32:19.000
Anything wrong?

00:32:19.040 --> 00:32:19.970
What did she say?

00:32:24.790 --> 00:32:25.590
Nothing much.

00:32:37.120 --> 00:32:38.250
I'll go make a report

00:32:38.680 --> 00:32:39.920
to the captain.

00:32:40.920 --> 00:32:42.240
Take them...

00:32:42.650 --> 00:32:43.930
to the bureau later.

00:32:45.810 --> 00:32:46.610
Officer Wang,

00:32:47.480 --> 00:32:48.960
is Yuhong in trouble or what?

00:32:48.960 --> 00:32:50.120
Mr. Qian, take it easy.

00:32:50.120 --> 00:32:52.120
The matter is under investigation.

00:32:56.150 --> 00:32:57.990
[Incoming call: Luo Bo]

00:32:58.590 --> 00:33:00.600
Chief Zhang, I need to take this call.

00:33:00.600 --> 00:33:01.920
Okay. Go ahead.

00:33:16.350 --> 00:33:17.280
What do you want?

00:33:17.680 --> 00:33:18.350
Tao,

00:33:19.970 --> 00:33:22.340
I've waited a long time
for a call from you.

00:33:23.050 --> 00:33:25.450
I heard
you guys took Yuhong's family away.

00:33:25.700 --> 00:33:26.810
That was quick.

00:33:27.620 --> 00:33:28.700
Stop harassing me.

00:33:28.720 --> 00:33:29.240
Listen,

00:33:29.260 --> 00:33:30.670
you won't get away this time.

00:33:30.670 --> 00:33:32.200
That had better not happen.

00:33:32.840 --> 00:33:34.170
Should I get in trouble,

00:33:34.270 --> 00:33:36.740
how can your mother
receive a kidney transplant?

00:33:36.740 --> 00:33:38.300
I've found a kidney for her.

00:33:39.350 --> 00:33:40.280
Will you take it?

00:33:43.270 --> 00:33:44.810
Hand over Qian Yuhong's family

00:33:44.810 --> 00:33:45.690
to me,

00:33:45.900 --> 00:33:48.740
and I'll arrange a surgery
for your mother right away.

00:33:48.740 --> 00:33:51.000
A suitable kidney is really hard to find.

00:33:51.550 --> 00:33:53.680
Give some serious thought to my offer.

00:34:16.320 --> 00:34:17.250
Eyes on the road.

00:34:18.230 --> 00:34:19.030
Try some peanuts.

00:34:19.030 --> 00:34:19.889
They're tasty.

00:34:19.989 --> 00:34:20.830
Let me try.

00:34:20.900 --> 00:34:21.570
Me too.

00:34:21.600 --> 00:34:22.909
Don't grab them all. Save me some!

00:34:22.909 --> 00:34:23.969
Sure. Here you are.

00:34:24.800 --> 00:34:26.530
Thank you so much, Peng.

00:34:26.710 --> 00:34:27.670
Without your help,

00:34:27.670 --> 00:34:28.600
we couldn't have

00:34:28.670 --> 00:34:29.980
secured a warehouse and a car.

00:34:29.980 --> 00:34:31.550
We're partners now.

00:34:31.550 --> 00:34:32.880
Why mention that at all?

00:34:33.070 --> 00:34:34.400
I only did what I should.

00:34:34.920 --> 00:34:35.590
What did you say?

00:34:35.590 --> 00:34:36.320
I only did what I should.

00:34:36.320 --> 00:34:37.400
We can't take your help for granted.

00:34:37.400 --> 00:34:38.510
Thanks should be given when due,

00:34:38.510 --> 00:34:39.030
right?

00:34:39.840 --> 00:34:40.770
You're welcome.

00:34:41.070 --> 00:34:41.550
Try one.

00:34:42.280 --> 00:34:44.230
Cheer up. Put on a smile.

00:34:44.710 --> 00:34:45.760
How rigid of you.

00:34:52.550 --> 00:34:53.280
Nice peanuts.

00:34:53.280 --> 00:34:54.260
Delicious.

00:34:54.960 --> 00:34:55.510
Tianye,

00:34:55.630 --> 00:34:56.280
bad news.

00:34:56.280 --> 00:34:57.480
Qian Yuhong has fled.

00:34:57.590 --> 00:34:59.320
Luo Bo sent Song Hao to find her.

00:34:59.840 --> 00:35:00.640
Where are you?

00:35:01.000 --> 00:35:02.470
Guanlan Residence, North Zhongshan Road.

00:35:02.470 --> 00:35:03.270
Come here now!

00:35:07.190 --> 00:35:07.880
Tianfei.

00:35:08.960 --> 00:35:09.760
What's wrong?

00:35:13.800 --> 00:35:14.460
Jiangyong,

00:35:14.590 --> 00:35:15.920
can you drive to Guanlan Residence,

00:35:15.920 --> 00:35:17.180
North Zhongshan Road?

00:35:19.590 --> 00:35:20.150
Tianye,

00:35:21.400 --> 00:35:23.440
are you hiding something from us?

00:35:26.400 --> 00:35:28.330
What is it with you? Say something!

00:35:46.480 --> 00:35:47.610
Why are you all here?

00:35:48.070 --> 00:35:48.590
Tianye,

00:35:49.550 --> 00:35:50.880
they know the truth now?

00:35:51.480 --> 00:35:53.810
Why didn't you discuss this with us first?

00:35:54.230 --> 00:35:55.700
Involving Fei in this

00:35:55.760 --> 00:35:57.210
is putting him in danger!

00:35:57.320 --> 00:35:58.780
It's fine. I'm not afraid.

00:35:59.230 --> 00:36:00.770
My acting was pretty good, wasn't it?

00:36:00.770 --> 00:36:01.670
Jiangyong, you...

00:36:01.670 --> 00:36:02.480
even hit me.

00:36:03.150 --> 00:36:04.130
Cut it out.

00:36:05.280 --> 00:36:06.480
I have no choice now.

00:36:07.230 --> 00:36:08.830
Since we're on the same boat,

00:36:09.230 --> 00:36:11.090
I might as well be honest with you.

00:36:12.000 --> 00:36:12.860
Stop being mad.

00:36:15.850 --> 00:36:17.310
What's the situation now?

00:36:18.070 --> 00:36:20.070
Look at that place with the light on.

00:36:20.800 --> 00:36:22.710
Song Hao has been up there for a while.

00:36:22.710 --> 00:36:23.720
I guess

00:36:23.880 --> 00:36:24.940
Yuhong is in there.

00:36:25.230 --> 00:36:26.360
But this is strange.

00:36:26.400 --> 00:36:27.320
What are they doing

00:36:27.320 --> 00:36:29.230
in this undelivered residential project?

00:36:29.230 --> 00:36:29.840
Tianye,

00:36:31.440 --> 00:36:32.170
how about...

00:36:32.470 --> 00:36:33.670
giving a call to Feng?

00:36:36.550 --> 00:36:38.010
Not after an observation.

00:36:53.440 --> 00:36:55.100
I don't think she's been here.

00:37:03.300 --> 00:37:05.500
Does she have any other dwelling place?

00:37:06.030 --> 00:37:08.440
She has several more properties
in Hanzhou.

00:37:08.440 --> 00:37:10.170
We'll check them out one by one.

00:37:39.440 --> 00:37:40.000
Tianye,

00:37:40.960 --> 00:37:42.220
shall we go after them?

00:37:43.630 --> 00:37:45.090
Let's go up and take a look.

00:38:53.400 --> 00:38:54.150
It's empty.

00:38:55.590 --> 00:38:56.850
What a waste of effort.

00:39:04.630 --> 00:39:06.290
Isn't this a wild goose chase?

00:39:28.070 --> 00:39:28.880
What was that about?

00:39:28.880 --> 00:39:29.880
You startled me!

00:39:35.400 --> 00:39:37.000
Is this authentic or fake?

00:39:47.630 --> 00:39:49.280
What's in this box?

00:39:53.840 --> 00:39:54.640
It's so heavy.

00:39:55.580 --> 00:39:57.860
[Gold Bar for Investment]